Class EstimoteException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • com.estimote.coresdk.common.exception.EstimoteException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EstimoteCloudException, EstimoteDeviceException

    public class EstimoteException
extends java.lang.RuntimeException
    A base class for all exceptions in the Estimote SDK.

    You can catch this instead of subclasses when you want to deal with exceptions in a generic way.

    Author:
    wiktor@estimote.com (Wiktor Gworek)
